header.hero-header
  a.canvs-login(href="http://canvs.tv/login") Login
    span.login-icon
      img(src="images/user-icon.svg")
  div.container
    div.hero-header-content
      div.branding-wrap
        p.logo-introducing Introducing
        a.canvs-logo-link(href="/")
          img.canvs-logo(src="images/logos/canvs-logo-white.svg")
          div.powered-by-wrap
            span.powered-by powered by
            img.mashwork-logo(src="images/logos/mashwork-logo-white-red.svg")

      h1.site-header The next generation in social TV analytics.

      a.video-play-btn(href='#', data-featherlight=".canvs-video")
        img.play-btn-triangle(src="images/play-btn-triangle.svg")

    button.action-btn.learn-more-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Learn More

section.about-canvs-section
  div.container
    div.row
      div.content-box.about-canvs-box.stop-counting
        img.about-canvs-illustration(src="images/stop-counting.svg")
        h2 Stop counting.
        p 
          strong You know how many people are talking about your show, but only Canvs can tell you why they’re talking about it. 
          | Canvs allows you to immediately identify the specific moments that drove audience reactions to your content. 
      div.content-box.about-canvs-box.forget-sentiment
        img.about-canvs-illustration(src="images/forget-sentiment.svg")
        h2 Forget sentiment.
        p 
          strong We know that social media sentiment tools aren’t accurate because we’ve used them all.
          | We don’t even believe in positive, negative, and neutral sentiment. Canvs uncovers nuanced audience emotions and lets you decide what they mean for your show. 

    button.action-btn.request-demo-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Request a Demo

section.updates-section
  div.container
    header.section-header-wrap
      h1.section-header Updates
      p.section-description The latest and greatest Canvs news

    a.updates-btn.blog-btn(href='http://mashwork.com/blog') Visit our Blog
    a.updates-btn.newsletter-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Get our Newsletter

section.actionable-insights-section
  div.container
    div.row
      header.section-header-wrap
        h1.section-header Actionable insights<br>for the TV ecosystem.
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/marketing-icon.svg")
        h2 Marketing
        p You know how many people are talking about your show, but only Canvs can automatically tell you what they’re feeling. 
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/adsales-icon.svg")
        h2 Ad Sales
        p Use Canvs to identify what other brands your most engaged audience loves. Then get to work selling super effective spots and integrations. 
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/production-icon.svg")
        h2 Production
        p Use Canvs to get feedback in real time. Know immediately if that joke in the third act landed and if viewers hate the new villain as much as you want them to.

    button.action-btn.get-started-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Get started with Canvs

section.single-solution-section
  div.container
    div.row
      header.section-header-wrap
        h1.section-header A single solution for<br>everything you want.
      div.content-box.single-solution-box.immediate-box
        img.single-solution-illustration(src="images/immediate-icon.svg")
        h2 Immediate
        p 
          strong No more settling for shaky sentiment. 
          | No more hours manually calculating it yourself. Canvs gives you immediate, actionable insights about how your audience feels with the click of a mouse.
      div.content-box.single-solution-box.credible-box
        img.single-solution-illustration(src="images/credible-icon.svg")
        h2 Credible
        p 
          strong Our pedigree speaks for itself: 
          | Canvs was built by New York City’s best social TV analysts and data scientists as a tool for themselves. See what it can do for you. 

    div.row
      div.content-box.single-solution-box.transparent-box
        img.single-solution-illustration(src="images/transparent-icon.svg")
        h2 Transparent
        p 
          strong Canvs gives you visibility into all conversation 
          | so you can see that Canvs is really as good at categorizing reactions as we say it is.
      div.content-box.single-solution-box.credible-box
        img.single-solution-illustration(src="images/beautiful-icon.svg")
        h2 Beautiful
        p 
          strong Gone are crowded dashboards and illegible charts. 
          | Canvs is clean, intuitive, and fun to use.
    div.row
      div.content-box.single-solution-box.intelligent-box
        img.single-solution-illustration(src="images/intelligent-icon.svg")
        h2 Intelligent
        p 
          strong Canvs was conceived in 2010 by some of the best minds in data science. 
          | Our expert analysts continually teach the platform the ever-evolving vernacular of social media. The result is a dynamically intelligent tool that reflects the real people are talking right now.

    a.action-btn.info-sheet-btn(href='/files/Canvs_Info_Sheet.pdf') Canvs Info Sheet

